extends layout

block head
  style.
    .col { margin-top: 16px;}

block content
  div.container
    div.row
      div.col.col-sm-12
        h1 Ozmo's Production Tool
        h6 Version: #{version}
        p Ozmo's Production Tool is designed to make a streaming a bit easier for Heroes of the Storm(tm).
            | The goal of the project is to allow streamers fast and easy access to the
            | graphical capabilities provided and animations allowed by HTML5/CSS/Javascript
            | without having to write or learn Flash or After Effects.

    div.row
      div.col.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
        div(role='alert').alert.alert-warning
          i.fa.fa-warning
          strong.spacer Warning!
          span Ozmo's Production Tool is in ALPHA. Bugs are expected, try reloading first. You can report issues
            a(href='https://github.com/jnovack/ozmos-production-tool/issues').spacer here
            | if you are having trouble.

    div.row
      div.col.col-sm-12
        h4 Live Draft
        p The Live Draft tool will interface with an active drafting session and display a clean and customizable
          | observer interface designed for broadcast.
      div.col.col-sm-8.col-sm-offset-2
        div(role='alert').alert.alert-info
          i.fa.fa-exclamation-circle
          strong.spacer Heads Up!
          span Observer interfaces look best in the latest Chrome at 1920x1080 (1080p).
      div.col.col-sm-12.text-center
        div.btn-toolbar
          a(data-group='draft-command-pills',href='/demo/livedraft').btn.btn-lg.btn-info
            i.fa.fa-magic
            | View Demo Draft
          a(data-group='draft-command-pills',href='/create/livedraft').btn.btn-lg.btn-success
            i.fa.fa-plus
            | Create Live Draft